message:
In the United States of America 83% of Sex Trafficking Victims  are identified as U.S Citizens. 
Domestic minor sex trafficking is a rapidly growing problem in the US. Greater Awareness and Education are needed in our communities. 
Learn more about Sex Trafficking on our website helperase.org or Google sex trafficking and the state you live in. Sharing what you’ve learned with others will help multiply the awareness.
